title 'Check for Understanding'

markdown <<MARKDOWN
Which of the following are infinite loops?

```
I.   for (int = 0; i < 0; i++) {
        System.out.println(i);
     }

II.  int i = 0;
     while (i < 1) {
        System.out.println(i);
     }

III. int i = 0;
     while (i < 10) {
        System.out.println(i);
        i--;
     }
```
MARKDOWN

wrong 'I only'
wrong 'II only'
wrong 'III only'
wrong 'I and II'
right 'II and III'
